Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡念咒語嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.99,0:02:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在午休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天回來晚了不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯…很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這些嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你打電話打擾到你了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起去喝點什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 今天有些應酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別喝太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你酒量不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那掛斷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然打電話過來  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見 努力工作哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對遙是責任感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的女朋友是水月你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  他在準備幽會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種正忙得不可開交的午飯時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏賊兮兮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.56,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只有讓他嘗嘗「天誅」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  天誅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫光他衣服拖著去遊街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他在這個街區再也呆不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.13,0:03:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦？這個很有趣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼拖誰去遊街？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有工作呢  快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是說拖出去遊街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很長的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀 真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克制自己的七情六欲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學生時代固然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步入社會卻只有弊大於利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要把事情想得太複雜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則  進展順利的事也會受阻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來就這麼不幸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼慘嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於看到你像個正常人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚痛快地玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探視時間已經過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工時間延長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你對涼宮做過什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 文緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  天川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是不是作了什麼約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一起念了咒語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咒語？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"唧唧嗚嗚啪"這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過差不多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙告訴你的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有詳細地說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過提起的時候看上去很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她記得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近涼宮的認知力めきめき恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0250,,{\fs10}注：めきめき有兩個意思，一個是快\N另一個是骨頭或樹木折斷的聲音\N這裏文緒誤解成後者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用“めきめき”不覺得奇怪嗎？ 天川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那めりめり
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0270,,{\fs10}注：めりめり表示樹木或骨頭慢慢被拗斷時發出的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那むきむき？（むきむき：各種方面）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,もりもり？（もりもり：狼吞虎嚥的樣子）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.04,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,もりもり？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是好勢頭吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對遙來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也多虧了男朋友呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 鳴海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很晚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在能去看她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在等你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是來了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上有什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚熬夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有點發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 對身體可不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得學習有點意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正離考試還有段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 會注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得無聊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.11,0:07:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你臉上寫著無聊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的"對不起"也差不多聽膩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  獻醜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨的演唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上司的命令   上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唱歌不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一起唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡情的唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把心裏的不痛快都發洩出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼誰來點歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 又要念咒語嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡你這麼說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 念咒語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喝得太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 喝太多了  前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆點了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.61,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使兩人無法牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們依然牢記…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我包忘了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過分的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.23,0:11:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西怎麼不對了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海喜歡的不是姐姐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說姐姐想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.70,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要再玩弄姐姐的感情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.77,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.35,0:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…其實我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 喝醉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在研究呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近太忙 你是不是忘了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙好像也在漸漸好轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得也該決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到一套好的房子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…雖然有點貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.37,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人合夥的話應該能買下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離車站也很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和這裏一樣是最邊上的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個週末一起去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.35,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先給房產商打個電話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要到週末才決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就打電話確認～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果週末去 週六還是周日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我休息 哪天都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘量快點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那週六吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是周日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬家…還不需要這麼急吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到遙的事告一段落也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說 說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.37,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要搬家的不是孝之嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.66,0:13:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是孝之說一起住嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以等遙她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這和遙的事告一段落什麼的\N根本沒關係吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們之間的問題吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼脾氣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發脾氣 當然要發脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有說不搬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候跟她說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和孝之的事情什麼時候和遙說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本就不想說吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不出口吧 是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明酒量不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還喝成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  我為什麼不能喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醉了又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我好難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我好痛苦啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明還喜歡她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之還是喜歡遙吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是真心話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是什麼真心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.90,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之根本就不愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之前輩 不怎麼精神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是幽會失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後對自己的無能感到喪氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒腔調  大笨牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海 正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介紹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.76,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SKY TEMPLE本部人事部伊藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是伊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好說到你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海 你說過你不是學生吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當中有什麼原委嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞人事的壞習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面就這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我還有事情忙 改天再來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他總是很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人事部的人來幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.27,0:17:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間店裏有一個人滿腦子只有幽會\N這一事實終於傳到本部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會影響到店的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以實地調查來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不炒這傢伙魷魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間店就沒有未來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這間店要關門？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是大件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也真是的  店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？  喪家犬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說影響形象的問題人物應該是這人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一個衝擊性的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連真由都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對著客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你點菜要點到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點  這個畜牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的臺詞哪里有形象
